## **ğŸ“Œ Best Practices for AWS Control Tower**  

âœ… **Use Organizational Units (OUs) Effectively** â€“ Group accounts based on function (e.g., Security, Dev, Production).  
âœ… **Apply Guardrails Early** â€“ Prevent security misconfigurations from the start.  
âœ… **Automate Account Creation** â€“ Use **Account Factory** to create accounts faster.  
âœ… **Monitor with AWS Security Hub** â€“ Regularly check security findings across accounts.  
âœ… **Use Centralized Billing** â€“ Consolidate AWS costs using **AWS Organizations**.  

